dct_title_s: Croatia city graphic 1:12,500. Split. Series M903
dct_description_sm: Alternate title: Split. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 20 meter and 10 meter (supplementary) contour intervals, and spot elevations. This sheet falls within NK 33-3, 1501, 1:250,000 and 2481 I, 2481 IV, 2482 II and 2482 III, M709, 1:50,000. Inset: map of area around Split airport (1:25,000). Map information as of 1993.
